PyAudio:
PyAudio provides python binding for portAudio the cross platform audio input library withpyaudio you can easily use python to play and record audio on avariety of platform 
Here To recognize the voice of user and to understand it we have to download and install the play audio file .

Download PyAudio from Python unofficial libraries
 
Select and download according to your system need 
 
Save it in same folder where main file is saved
  
